{"tid":1612471,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[認清現實] 革命已經降臨　我地冇得返轉頭","createTime":"2019-10-02T09:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T13:17:20.000Z","uid":15224,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"51a55769c729c6e7836a30cef42cff647bfb6475","tid":1612471,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:05:44.000Z","msg":"唔明你地咁撚嬲做乜, 真心膠期望D恐怖份子會認錯咩? 香港黑警仲賤撚過恐怖份子永遠唔會承認責任, 由 DAY1起 累積咁多警暴, 而家實彈都開埋, 往後必然成常態, 步鎗掃射坦克碌豬不是夢呀, 班恐怖份子高層當然要撐到行, 黑都講成白架啦, 仲期望佢割咩? 笑話<br />\n<br />\n冇架喇, 根本而家發展到 &quot;唔係你死就我亡&quot; 既局面, 一係清算政府同狗隊, 一係俾佢地清算我地種族清洗, 請認清現實, 武裝自己心態, 革命臨降左架喇, 我地冇得返轉頭, 行動係最撚實際, 諗下點復仇好過啦"},{"pid":"f371a5a3fbf8f67ba0e09462b3b664f8361c6bb2","tid":1612471,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59ac065eca02fb47adb4094fef221bf325a0da0","tid":1612471,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d2d84b50ffc5ee2913fc93948f561f1b66d7a7","tid":1612471,"uid":25002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:18:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c1d50bea6a8a888fb44002727eb24dd644d7c1c","tid":1612471,"uid":254123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:18:44.000Z","msg":"以後勇武行動應全面地下化及各區開花，遊行集會留畀和理非做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609107</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"70c8f639fe5f3e5dd05a2a9fb4b0a039e2fabb77","tid":1612471,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:19:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40e0eb13081ebcfd9723b327ca0947bfc37c5b5","tid":1612471,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67527f811f63ef47fbeab3b35104966b32a801cc","tid":1612471,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:26:42.000Z","msg":"一定要贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5871923bc69c443991cac06837580b33c52b7ad8","tid":1612471,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T09:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d436081fcd7f8b9f88122fa87c48b8d4b48b030d","tid":1612471,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad66658812996133ebf2d3df0bec348516bfff1f","tid":1612471,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:02:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">倡新制度: 去「中心化」取代「共產」以及「neoliberalism全球化的資本主義」： </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n共產主義問題:<br />\n1)不重視傳統文化同身份，因為共產主義擁有自己的文化與文學。<br />\n2)消滅私有產權。<br />\n3)個人不能擁有生產力，農民必須把私有的土地和耕畜，大型農具等主要生產資料轉為合作社集體所有，國家控制生產工具同生產資料再按需求去分配工作。<br />\n<br />\n而資本主義平問題說穿了，就是 弱肉強食 跟 社會達爾文主義 。物極必反，最終會造成貧富差距越來越大，根本問題是由全球化加上新自由主意的資本主義所引發，令有錢人可以令自己有更大優勢賺更多錢，從而出現壟斷令市場失效。<br />\n<br />\n正是因有馬太效應，有資本主義就有剝削同貧富懸殊，貧富差距越來越大，這就是馬太效應貧富差距的擴大，不因為多數的人意志而轉移，依然我行我素。<br />\n這就是馬太效應，反映強者愈強、弱者愈弱的現象。<br />\n<br />\n舉例2013年，美國<br />\n前0.1%的人口，占據全國22%的財富；<br />\n前10%的人口，占據全國77%的財富；<br />\n後90%的人口，占據全國23%的財富。<br />\n<br />\n又例如，公平市場就好像是一場公平考試，但其實評分標準都只是拉完curve再定個標準，永遠只有少數占據全國的大部分財富。<br />\n<br />\n而Ontic的去中心化，提倡淡化資源分配角色的權力才是出路，令大部份人可以從事自己的興趣有關的工作。另一方面群眾可花大量時間去學習或創業，進而不斷尋求新的刺激和新的發現。<br />\n互聯網其實已經啟動這個進程，互聯網本來就是去中心化協調機制，一旦&quot;大台&quot;如司令部，行政中樞被毀， 散落不同地點的部門機關依然可以繼續協調操作。在網路技術未出現年代，如現在這種&quot;無大台&quot;是不可能的事，所有政治活動都要有中樞總籌物資同行動，孫中山也不可能上網打字就可以跟同志溝通，一定要有一個人人信服的組織, i.e. 大台來統一指揮調動。Ontic的去中心化也有類似於勢力平衡論想法，但係以多個目標但又互相配合為目的。而勢力平衡論想法需要一個共存共榮為目標。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一節 時代與環境：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=970985116579330&amp;id=408394076171773&amp;__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D970985116579330%26id%3D408394076171773%26__tn__%3D-R&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2Bmu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=27e901b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=970985116579330&amp;id=408394076171773&amp;__tn__=-R</a><br />\n<br />\n第二節 現代制度的缺陷:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=970984906579351&amp;id=408394076171773&amp;__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D970984906579351%26id%3D408394076171773%26__tn__%3D-R&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2Bmu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=11d74415\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=970984906579351&amp;id=408394076171773&amp;__tn__=-R</a><br />\n<br />\n第三節 新制度的構想:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=970984549912720&amp;id=408394076171773&amp;__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D970984549912720%26id%3D408394076171773%26__tn__%3D-R&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2Bmu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=ed3bc466\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=970984549912720&amp;id=408394076171773&amp;__tn__=-R</a><br />\n<br />\n第四節 名利權論:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=970983399912835&amp;id=408394076171773&amp;__tn__=-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D970983399912835%26id%3D408394076171773%26__tn__%3D-R&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2Bmu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=c906ab7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=970983399912835&amp;id=408394076171773&amp;__tn__=-R</a><br />\n<br />\nFloatCityV專頁（可以利用FloatCityV在海外建立新領土，實行新制）<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FloatCityv-123505392377024/?modal=admin_todo_tour\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFloatCityv-123505392377024%2F%3Fmodal%3Dadmin_todo_tour&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2Bmu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=3ec72261\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FloatCityv-123505392377024/?modal=admin_todo_tour</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\nFloatCityV TG：大家如興趣可以加入FloatCityV出謀劃策。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LERSsRIsuYFLJ08KrMfqQQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLERSsRIsuYFLJ08KrMfqQQ&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2Bmu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=3f4c8804\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LERSsRIsuYFLJ08KrMfqQQ</a><br />\n<br />\n新加坡人 同 美國加州機構 合作 建立首個「海上國家」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1499809/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1499809/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人之路：（與白人達到真正平等的必備）<br />\n<br />\n1.倡新制度Ontic的去中心化；<br />\n2.倡西學，「復興」漢學；<br />\n3.倡&ldquo;孝道&rdquo;因其實本身只是一種倫理道德，但要摒棄古代中國的一種孝道政治制度。<br />\n<br />\n香港人算是黃種人裏國際化、素質等最高的了，但也只有青年人的自主意識高於歐美平均水平，其他年齡人低於甚至遠低於歐美平均水平，奴性較重。 <br />\n<br />\n華人或黃種人裏的最大群體是中國人（大陸人），但現今大陸人的自主獨立意識及環境可能還趕不上100年前的五四新文化時期，這說明了CCP的愚忠教育非常成功，同時華人或黃種人的前途非常不妙。照此下去，可能會有《排華法案》等重現。 <br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，共產主義所引發的獨裁問題相當之明顯，共產主義是一個科學化的獨裁方法，人類歷史上不少國家已經實驗過，單是中國犧牲千千萬萬人命，結果演變成今日嘅社會主義怪胎。"},{"pid":"846499bb367a015f701f68b0689f037d2837a046","tid":1612471,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:09:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eee61c730d90003f12263098704030850ffcb18b","tid":1612471,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd0efa7413e1667ab0efa100fde6b8fe3db372e4","tid":1612471,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae2f462ccc71eb484120f5fc1ff2fea9594d2da","tid":1612471,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:08:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32baee4cfe3ed171858df8f6149da7133cce7c4a","tid":1612471,"uid":318839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:17:20.000Z","msg":"推，要推到國際認定香港警察係恐怖組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}